data.description: Welcome to this beautiful bi-level in Canfield. Sitting on almost a half acre, this 3 bedroom, 3 bath home has many updates. Through the front door you will find a large foyer, living room ,dining area and kitchen. The Kitchen has beautiful cabinets , neutral back splash,and movable island. family room, laundry room , and half bathroom complete the lower level. Upstairs the hall bathroom is complete with a new tub, glass enclosure, timeless ceramic tile to the ceiling, new vanity with a linen cabinet , vinyl wood flooring. The master has a ample closet space, and a master bathroom with the same vinyl flooring, walk-in shower , new vanity and lighting. 2 more bedrooms complete the upper floor. A large concrete pad is located off the sliding glass door and is ready for entertaining! Attached 2 car garage with storage cabinets also has a door leading out the the backyard. Many updates included, Carpeting throughout, foyer and kitchen flooring, bathroom flooring, fresh paint throughout along with, New roof - 2019 Furnace and A/C - 2020 Hot water tank- 2019
